abstractProcessModelSets.name: Holistic Client App Kernel: d2r2/React Client Display Adapter
abstractProcessModelSets.description: Manages the details of initializing and dynamically updating the client application view (DOM display surface) via @encapsule/d2r2 and Facebook React.

controllerActionSets.name: Holistic App Client Display Adapter: Initialize Display Layout
controllerActionSets.description: Performs initial programmatic re-render of the display adapter's DIV target using d2r2 <ComponentRouter/> and a copy of the d2r2 renderData that the app server process used to render the static HTML5 content that resides currently in the display adapter's DIV target element.

controllerActionSets.name: Holistic App Client Display Adapter: Process Step Worker
controllerActionSets.description: Performs actions on behalf of the Holistic App Client Display Adapter process.

controllerActionSets.name: Holistic App Client Display Adapter: Update Display Layout
controllerActionSets.description: Performs a programmatic re-rendering of the display adapter's DIV target using d2r2 <ComponentRouter/>.
